1. In the window SelectMeals, 
- a button to change years (next/previous year)
- a button to change months (next/previous month). Of course, changing months may 
also imply to change a year.
- a label that indicates which is the year of the visible week.
- a label that indicates which is the month of the first day of the visible week.

2. In the window EditUserWI
- a button to modify user-periods:
* a user-period can be always extended (if does not overlap with an existing period).
* a user-period can be shortened, but:
- never beyond now()
- never if there is a (non-empty) dailyMealSelection for this user for the part of
the period that is intended to cut.

